{"type": "article", "id": 12714, "title": "2015 的秋冬大片，奢侈品们都在拍些啥？", "description": "Dior 请了“乌云密布”来帮忙，Saint Laurent 走了朋克风。\r\n", "date": "2015-07-28T15:20:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13573, "name": "秋冬大片"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607135942XpYiVGbohe1WqaTM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t时尚界总是不能安分过当季。盛夏虽在，各大奢侈品已开始纷纷推出秋季大片。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t我们为你挑了 7 个大牌拍的美片，看一看吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t1.  Dior 去了诺曼底，还请了“乌云密布”来帮忙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135933KrUhnoP1dJGTsi9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135933W4BQDw86p3FEtjSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135934VdF3nZNOYl8Stp1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t2.  Miu Miu 去了大街上找灵感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135935fK9HXc7WFlZivdQe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59832246\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713593526ESxKM0vNZ8PDuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59421642\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071359363aYoTGQXUk9gli45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5931418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135936ZgoSR7bLr4CQnlYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58736059\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t3.  <span style=\"text-align:start;\">尽管分道扬镳、吵吵闹闹，<a href=\"http://www.style.com/trends/industry/2015/gucci-fall-2015-ads\" target=\"_blank\">Gucci 的这些设计还是前任设计总监 Frida Giannini 的作品。</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135937J8neZily2k6aQtxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135937GK5uvHAUY6c0C2Im.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071359385ePbnBJAjpdmGalf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135938VkAv0SpKUPGqmZng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t4.  <a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/07/chanel-fall-2015-ad-campaign\" target=\"_blank\">Chanel 这次选了黑白只为突出衣服的质地</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135939R318u5fgG6DUE9XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135939jGzSgxALIDXqiapt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t5.  Prada 的新面孔和新发型。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135940knFGoy3Etd4gueWB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135940UX5kfThoScMx7mqw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135941bsLVlM102Rwky8om.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t7.  这一次，<span>Dolice</span><span style=\"text-align:left;background-color:transparent;\"> &amp; Gabbana 没让模特们</span>跳<span style=\"text-align:start;\">弗拉明戈，但似乎拍了个全家福？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135941E3HiZU7lKFWGJRvT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135942tlh72Pz6y3wpYacq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67008388\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}